Long-term outcomes of third-line therapy with tyrosine kinase inhibitors in 
chronic phase chronic myeloid leukemia: A real-life experience.

Chitanava T(1), Matvienko I(1), Shuvaev V(2), Voloshin S(3), Martynkevich I(4), 
Vlasova Y(5), Efremova E(3), Mileeva E(2), Pirkhalo A(2), Makarova T(1), Vlasik 
R(1), Karyagina E(6), Il Ina N(7), Medvedeva N(8), Dorofeeva N(8), Shneider 
