The health impact of long COVID during the 2021-2022 Omicron wave in Australia: 
a quantitative burden of disease study.

Howe S(1), Szanyi J(1), Blakely T(1).

Author information:
(1)Population Interventions Unit, Centre for Epidemiology and Biostatistics, 
Melbourne School of Population and Global Health, University of Melbourne, 
